Class Path

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.common.Path
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Path>

    public class Path
extends Object
implements Comparable<Path>
    Path object for handling pathes. A path consists of several path parts. The String representation uses the > as separator between path elements.
    Author:
    pnientiedt
